                (KvK)
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>KvK-nummer:</strong> [KVK_NUMMER]
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>BTW-nummer:</strong> [BTW_NUMMER]
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>Adres:</strong> [UW_ADRES]
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>E-mail:</strong> [UW_EMAIL]
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                <strong>Telefoon:</strong> +31 6 42221525
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Onze diensten</h2>
