            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
              <li>Onze website</li>
              <li>WhatsApp: +31 6 42221525</li>
              <li>E-mail: [UW_EMAIL]</li>
              <li>Instagram of Facebook</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 mt-6">
              4.2 Betalingsvoorwaarden
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              <strong>[SPECIFICEER UW BETALINGSBELEID]</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
              <li>
                Volledige vooruitbetaling is vereist om de boeking te
